{"tid":1328821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位 張超雄單野請聽我再講一次","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:26:29.000Z","uid":274289,"like":41,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"abd29ef289e91e0d727e627f2cbc84b40ecfc7db","tid":1328821,"uid":274289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:39:40.000Z","msg":"根本換湯唔換藥<br />\n佢話如果建制將條例改到面眸全非會立刻撒回？<br />\n你張超雄憑乜野要全香港人一個月既努力押係你一個身上？<br />\n況且成功只係proof到所謂林鄭惺惺作態利益用陳同佳案<br />\n呢點其實已經好撚清楚 唔需要你攪咁多野補充<br />\n<br />\n唔撚明點解有人為左唔割席就支持<br />\n<br />\n呢野成本好大<br />\n潛在效益好少！<br />\n<br />\n醒呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9b34f079a4ebb3d04d23dc0e22121293da2500","tid":1328821,"uid":8349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd8e42d5d15bf549cbcf83b6c93378dc6762886","tid":1328821,"uid":8349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804e005fd35d84e69a5836d2e1613a91ec18d8b0","tid":1328821,"uid":8349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ae039fdc80b8927d39f4bd52c2c784d4b99518","tid":1328821,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【杜絕分化】熱狗惡行 24小時輪流廣播 （2）</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295085\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Blocked 上一頁</span></span>"},{"pid":"5096b1af95cbc8a661aed2f9f76567c129f84aa3","tid":1328821,"uid":274289,"like":0,"dislike":0